OL,3,CBereaved parents secure political
OL,4,Csupport for their 'duty of care' fight
OL,6,FIn a debate at Westminster on Tuesday
OL,7,FJanuary 13th there was cross-party
OL,8,Fsupport for their campaign from a
OL,9,Frange of MPs, giving the couple hope
OL,10,Fthey can get the law changed.
OL,12,FThe Government, however, maintains a
OL,13,Fstatutory 'duty of care' could be a
OL,14,Fdisproportionate response.
OL,16,FNatasha, who was from Nottinghamshire,
OL,17,Ftook her own life in April 2018 on the
OL,18,Fday she was due to take part in a
OL,19,Fgroup presentation at the University
OL,20,Fof Bristol.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
