OL,3,CBereaved parents secure political
OL,4,Csupport for their 'duty of care' fight
OL,6,FThe 20-year-old had been suffering
OL,7,Ffrom chronic social anxiety disorder.
OL,8,FIn 2024, the High Court found the
OL,9,Funiversity contributed to Ms
OL,10,FAbrahart's death by discriminating
OL,11,Fagainst her.
OL,13,FIn 2022, a judge ruled the university
OL,14,Fdiscriminated against Ms Abrahart by
OL,15,Ffailing to accommodate her mental
OL,16,Fhealth disability, and make
OL,17,F"reasonable adjustments".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
