OL,6,F"Natasha would support anything that
OL,7,Fwould make life better for students.
OL,8,FShe would never want anyone to suffer
OL,9,Fthe way she suffered."
OL,11,FNatasha's father, Bob, said: "Natasha
OL,12,Fwas a really caring person,
OL,13,Funiversities need to be more like
OL,14,FNatasha."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
