OL,6,FReferencing the debate, Mr Abrahart
OL,7,Fadded: "What we saw was really
OL,8,Finteresting, we didn't just have
OL,9,FLabour MPs backing it, we also had
OL,10,FLiberal Democrats, and the
OL,11,FConservatives backing us. The
OL,12,Flandscape is changing."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
