OL,3,CBereaved parents secure political
OL,4,Csupport for their 'duty of care' fight
OL,6,FThe Government acknowledged there are
OL,7,Fproblems with universities across the
OL,8,FUK, but voiced concerns that the
OL,9,Fintroduction of a statutory 'duty of
OL,10,Fcare' could be a disproportionate
OL,11,Fresponse - with them arguing that more
OL,12,Fyoung people take their lives in the
OL,13,Fgeneral population, than they do at
OL,14,Funiversity.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
