OL,3,CBereaved parents secure political
OL,4,Csupport for their 'duty of care' fight
OL,6,FUniversities UK, which is a collective
OL,7,Fvoice of universities across England,
OL,8,FScotland, Wales and Northern Ireland,
OL,9,Fsaid: "University leaders recognise
OL,10,Fthe profound impact that suicide has
OL,11,Fupon families, friends and the wider
OL,12,Funiversity community.
OL,14,F"We support the need to demonstrate
OL,15,Fprogress on student mental health,
OL,16,Fincluding against agreed sector
OL,17,Fframeworks, involving trusted
OL,18,Fcontacts, learning from mistakes, and,
OL,19,Fabove all, acting with transparency
OL,20,Fand compassion.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
